<p>I am using Adobe Muse. It automatically redirects a desktop home page to a mobile home page. However, I want this to redirect the whole domain to a mobile version. I want it to generate all addresses automatically.</p>  <p>For example:</p>  <pre><code>desktop:   example.com/blogpost1 redirects to: example.com/mobile/blogpost1 </code></pre>  <p>Another example:</p>  <pre><code>desktop:   example.com/about redirects to: example.com/mobile/about.. </code></pre>  <p>I want it to generate automatically <code>/mobile/</code> for all domains, if any mobile device is detected.</p>